<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/xdna-npu> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "AMD's neural processing unit at 50 TOPS on Strix Halo. Can handle prompt processing (prefill) for fast time-to-first-token while the iGPU handles token generation (decode). Model support is still limited compared to GPU; the NPU does not have access to the full memory bandwidth. Best for power-efficient inference of smaller models." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#hardware> ;
