<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/vulkan/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp/blob/master/docs/backend/VULKAN.md"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Vulkan GPU Inference" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/vulkan> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "GPU compute API via the RADV open-source driver. Currently faster than ROCm on Strix Halo for both prompt processing and token generation, and much easier to set up. The recommended backend for llama.cpp on Strix Halo as of early 2026." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#hardware> ;
