<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/vllm/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GitHub" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/vllm> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "High-throughput serving engine optimized for batched workloads. Supports PagedAttention for efficient KV cache management, AWQ and GPTQ quantization, continuous batching. OpenAI-compatible API. AMD ROCm support exists but less mature than llama.cpp. Better suited for multi-user server scenarios than single-user desktop inference." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#engines> ;
