<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/tabby/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://github.com/TabbyML/tabby"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GitHub" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/tabby> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Self-hosted code completion server (~33k GitHub stars). Runs entirely on your infrastructure with full data governance. Team-oriented with repository indexing. Good for fast inline completions powered by smaller local models while Claude Code handles complex tasks." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#assistants> ;
