<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/starcoder2> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "BigCode/ServiceNow's 15B code model. 16K context. Good for fill-in-the-middle (FIM) and autocomplete — the type of task Tabby and Continue.dev use for inline completions. Outclassed for chat-style coding by newer models." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#code-models> ;
