	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/rocm> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "AMD's open GPU compute platform. ROCm 7.x has performance regressions on Strix Halo — HIP barely outperforms CPU for prompt processing, with regressions at high context sizes. Workaround: compiler flag -mllvm --amdgpu-unroll-threshold-local=600. KV cache may get dumped to shared memory instead of VRAM. Flash attention (-fa 1) and --no-mmap are mandatory for stable usage." ;
