<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/qwen3-coder-next> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "80B MoE model with only 3B active parameters. 256K native context (1M with YaRN). Agentic-trained — comparable to Claude Sonnet on coding benchmarks. Uses ~46GB on unified memory. Excellent performance because only active parameters need bandwidth. Strong tool calling support." ;
