<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/qwen25-coder-32b> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Alibaba's flagship open code model. 32B parameters, 128K context. Matches or exceeds GPT-4o on HumanEval (~92%), MBPP (~85%). At Q8_0 uses ~34GB — near-lossless quality with room for full 128K context on 128GB hardware. The sweet spot for local code generation." ;
