<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/qwen25-72b> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Alibaba's top-tier general model. 72B parameters, 128K context with YaRN. HumanEval ~86%. At Q4_K_M uses ~45GB, Q6_K ~60GB. Competitive with GPT-4 on many benchmarks. Excellent for both code and general reasoning." ;
