<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/powerinfer> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Sparse heterogeneous GPU-CPU inference engine from SJTU-IPADS. Exploits power-law neuron activation: hot neurons on GPU, cold neurons on CPU. Up to 11.69x faster than llama.cpp. 13.20 tok/s on OPT-175B with single RTX 4090 (only 18% below A100). PowerInfer-2 targets smartphones." ;
