<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/phi-4> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Microsoft's compact reasoning model. 14B parameters, 16K context. HumanEval ~82% — remarkable for its size. At Q8_0 uses only ~15GB. Excellent as a fast draft/secondary model. Can run alongside a larger model without memory pressure." ;
