<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/ollama> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "User-friendly wrapper around llama.cpp with a CLI and REST API. Since v0.14.0 (January 2026), natively supports the Anthropic Messages API — enabling direct connection from Claude Code without a translation proxy. Model library is curated but extensive. Supports AMD GPUs via ROCm and Vulkan. The simplest path to running local models." ;
