	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Documentation" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/mlc-llm> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Machine learning compiler for universal LLM deployment via Apache TVM. Compiles models to run on CUDA, Vulkan, Metal, WebGPU (in-browser via WebLLM), iOS, Android. ML compilation optimizes per-target. WebLLM enables full in-browser inference with no server." ;
