<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/mixtral-8x22b> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Mistral's large MoE model. 141B total, 39B active parameters. 64K context. At Q4_K_M uses ~85GB — fits in 128GB but tight. Good general capability. The MoE architecture gives better quality per active parameter than dense models." ;
