<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/localai> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Open-source Go-based AI engine. Drop-in replacement for both OpenAI AND Anthropic APIs natively (since v3.10.0). Supports multiple backends: llama.cpp, vLLM, Transformers, ExLlama2. Handles text, image, audio, video, embeddings, TTS, function calling, and constrained grammars. The only engine besides Ollama that speaks Anthropic Messages API natively." ;
