<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/llamafile> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Single-file executable that bundles a model with the inference engine (based on llama.cpp + Cosmopolitan libc). Runs on any x86-64 or ARM64 OS without installation. Great for distribution and air-gapped deployments." ;
