<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/llama-cpp> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The foundational C/C++ inference engine for running LLMs on consumer hardware. Supports GGUF format, all quantization levels, multiple backends (CUDA, ROCm, Vulkan, Metal, CPU). Features KV cache quantization (Q4/Q8) that dramatically reduces context memory overhead. Includes llama-server for OpenAI-compatible HTTP API. The standard against which all other local inference is measured." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#engines> ;
