<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/llama-3.3-70b> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Meta's dense 70B model (December 2024). 128K context. Matches Llama 3.1 405B quality at 70B size. HumanEval ~82%. At Q5_K_M uses ~50GB, Q6_K ~58GB. Strong general-purpose + code capability. One of the best all-round models for 128GB hardware." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#general-models> ;
