<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/litellm> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Open-source proxy that translates between API formats. Sits between Claude Code and local/remote model servers. Provides load balancing, fallbacks, cost tracking, and model routing. Translates Anthropic Messages API to OpenAI-compatible format for backends that don't speak Anthropic natively. Security note: PyPI versions 1.82.7 and 1.82.8 were compromised with credential-stealing malware." ;
