<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/lemonade> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "AMD's lightweight native C++ inference service (2MB binary). Exposes OpenAI-compatible API at localhost:13305. Splits workload between NPU (prefill for fast time-to-first-token) and iGPU (decode for bandwidth). Purpose-built for AMD AI PCs including Strix Halo." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#engines> ;
