<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/kobold-cpp> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Single-file llama.cpp fork with integrated web UI. Focused on creative writing and roleplay but fully capable for code. Triple API: KoboldAI + OpenAI + Ollama compatible endpoints. Zero-install single executable with built-in memory and SillyTavern integration." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#engines> ;
