<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/huggingface> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/huggingface/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/huggingface/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://huggingface.co"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Website" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/huggingface> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Primary distribution platform for all open LLMs. All model families publish here. GGUF files hosted directly. Search for model name + 'GGUF' to find quantized versions. Has more quantization variety than the Ollama library." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#distribution> ;
