<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/gemini-cli/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GitHub" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/gemini-cli> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Google's open-source CLI coding assistant (Apache 2.0). Speaks the Gemini API natively. Can be pointed at local models via OpenAI-compatible endpoints using the --model flag with openai/ prefix. Leverages Gemini's large context windows (up to 1M tokens). Supports tool calling for file operations and shell commands. Includes built-in safety checks and sandboxed execution." ;
