<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/fine-tuning> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Adapting a pre-trained model to a specific task or domain by training it further on curated data. DeepSeek-R1 distills are fine-tuned versions of Llama/Qwen with reasoning traces. LoRA (Low-Rank Adaptation) is the most common method — it trains only a small number of additional parameters, making it feasible on consumer hardware. Unsloth provides optimized fine-tuning tools." ;
