<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/exl3> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "ExLlamaV3's next-gen format using QTIP-based Hadamard transforms and trellis encoding on 16x16 Tensor Core tiles. Coherent at 1.6 bits per weight — a 70B model in under 16GB VRAM. Marlin-inspired GEMM kernel approaches memory bandwidth limit at 4 bpw. NVIDIA CUDA only." ;
