<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/context-window> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The maximum number of tokens a model can process in a single request — input plus output. Measured in tokens (roughly 0.75 words each). Modern models range from 8K to 256K+ tokens. Longer context requires more memory for the KV cache (key-value pairs stored during attention). On 128GB hardware, a 70B model at 4-bit can practically use ~80-100K tokens before memory runs out." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#concepts> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Context Window" ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "context-window" ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf> ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#concept> , <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/codex> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/codex/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/codex/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://github.com/openai/codex"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GitHub" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/codex> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "OpenAI's open-source CLI coding assistant (Apache 2.0). Speaks the OpenAI Responses API natively. Can be pointed at local models via OPENAI_BASE_URL or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint. Supports tool calling for file reads, writes, and shell commands. Runs sandboxed by default — commands execute in a restricted environment. Requires models with function calling support for full functionality." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#assistants> ;
