<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/claude-code/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Documentation" ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/claude-code> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Anthropic's official CLI coding assistant. Speaks the Anthropic Messages API. Can be pointed at local models via ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL. Sends a ~16k token system prompt, so local models need 64k+ context. Supports /model for mid-session switching. Tool calling is the main pain point with local models — some engines drop tool call responses during streaming." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#assistants> ;
