<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/ccproxy> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Go-based proxy specifically designed for Claude Code. Intercepts and routes requests with intelligent model routing based on token count, tool usage, or custom rules. Can connect Claude Code to Ollama, OpenAI, GitHub Copilot, or Claude Pro/Max via OAuth." ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#proxies> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "CCProxy" ;
	<https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "ccproxy" ;
	<http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf> ;
	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#proxy> , <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/bifrost> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Lightweight API gateway for routing AI model requests. One of five commonly used gateways alongside LiteLLM, Cloudflare AI Gateway, Kong AI Gateway, and OpenRouter." ;
