<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/bartowski/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://huggingface.co/bartowski"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> ;
