	a <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/bartowski> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Currently the most active GGUF quantizer on HuggingFace. Covers nearly every new model release within hours. Provides multiple quant levels per model. Experiments with imatrix calibration and has contributed to llama.cpp quantization recipes." ;
