<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/local-llm-graph/rdf/node/aphrodite> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "vLLM-based engine by PygmalionAI with the broadest quantization support of any engine: AQLM, AWQ, BitNet, bitsandbytes, EETQ, GGUF, GPTQ, QuIP#, EXL2, Marlin, FP2-FP12, NVFP4, MXFP4, and more. OpenAI-compatible API. Context parallelism and dynamic model management. v0.10.0 (Nov 2025)." ;
